            . I am a broker, and live in Lon Alley, Shoreditch. On the 23th of July, the prisoner came<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182209110111"></xptr>and sold me a watering pot, which she said was her husband's. I accompanied her up the street to find her husband; she then said she had none, but would give me the watering pot to let her go. I gave her in charge. Another woman was with her.</p>
