                  </persName>
            . I am servant to Mr. Eames, the watering pot is his. I saw it safe a few days before it was stolen: I put the things out at the door every morning. I dont recollect seeing it there on the 20th of July. I missed it the morning the constable brought it.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. A woman asked me to go and sell it, as her husband was ill; I went with her and carried it, but she was to sell it.</p>
